BlueNMEA 2.1.3 - 2011-09-01
* catch IllegalArgumentException while setting up the LocationListener
* Peer: work around NullPointerException
* work around IllegalArgumentException from dismissDialog()

BlueNMEA 2.1.2 - 2011-03-14
* don't restart on screen orientation changes

BlueNMEA 2.1.1 - 2011-02-02
* fix the "bearing" GPRMC column

BlueNMEA 2.1 - 2011-01-14
* provide a Bluetooth server (RFCOMM serial port)
* allow operation without native library
* hide the "Connect" button when Bluetooth is disabled
* click on a client disconnects it
* add menu option "Disconnect all"

BlueNMEA 2.0 - 2010-11-27
* Makefile: adapt to newest Android NDK r4b
* Main: show progress dialog while scanning
* listen on a TCP port (without Bluetooth)

BlueNMEA 1.2 - 2010-07-24
* fix N/S, E/W suffixes
* show error message when Bluetooth library isn't available
* better system error messages
  - print a helpful message when Bluetooth is disabled
* fix NullPointerException due to race condition
* fix IllegalStateException due to race condition

BlueNMEA 1.1 - 2010-02-17
* send $GPGSA/$GPGSV messages

BlueNMEA 1.0.1 - 2010-01-11
* fix for malformed negative latitude/longitude values

BlueNMEA 1.0 - 2009-08-27
* initial release
